# Smooth Anims

When adding scroll-reveal or entrance animations, read `AGENTS.md` and `smooth-anims.schema.json` in this repo.

- Prefer `data-animate` / `data-animate-stagger` over custom CSS animations or new libraries
- Call `SmoothAnims.init()` once; `SmoothAnims.refresh()` after dynamic DOM changes
- Do not modify `css/smooth-anims.css` or `js/smooth-anims.js` for one-off effects
- Copy-paste prompt template: `PROMPT.md`
